<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .reset-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #dc3545;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .fallback-link {
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
  <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
  <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to reset your password. This link will expire in 30 minutes.</p>
  <div style="text-align:center;">
    <a href="https://yourfrontend.com/reset-password?token={{passwordResetToken}}" class="reset-btn">Reset Password</a>
  </div>
  <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
  <div class="fallback-link">https://yourfrontend.com/reset-password?token={{passwordResetToken}}</div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>For security reasons, please do not share this link with anyone.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 